* This interface represents the volume of fluid passing a point in a system * per unit of time. The system unit for this quantity is "m³/s" * (cubic meter per second). Jean-Marie Dautelle 3.0, March 2, 2006
* Wikipedia: Volumetric Flow Rate
* Holds the SI unit (Système International d'Unités) for this quantity.
